too cold yesterday?

86
00:08:34,317 --> 00:08:35,885
You might have a slight fever.

87
00:08:35,885 --> 00:08:37,686
Don't worry.

88
00:08:38,554 --> 00:08:40,556
I took medicine.

89
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:43,593
