224
00:24:53,028 --> 00:24:54,795
Get away!

225
00:24:59,034 --> 00:25:01,235
Let me go!

226
00:25:03,238 --> 00:25:06,407
Let go!

227
00:25:07,743 --> 00:25:09,544
