231
00:25:14,316 --> 00:25:16,517
Bastard.

232
00:25:17,819 --> 00:25:21,455
You'd better pray I never...

233
00:25:22,324 --> 00:25:24,258
I never

234
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:27,061
find out who you are.

235
00:25:28,797 --> 00:25:31,465
