236
00:25:32,334 --> 00:25:34,602
You bastard.

237
00:25:35,470 --> 00:25:37,104
Be gentle.

238
00:25:50,619 --> 00:25:53,588
Clearly, he came this way...

239
00:25:54,389 --> 00:25:56,857
